Libraries
- use bun for installing dependencies and running tasks
- use tailwind for styling

Code Style
- Prefer named exports over default exports
- Prefer function declarations over arrow functions unless it can have an implicit return
- Use camelCase
- Use PascalCase for component names and enums
- Prefer tailwind clases over inline styles

Formatting
- Use consistent Tailwind class ordering 

Types
- Prefer interfaces over types
- Do not use "any" in TypeScript
- Use React.PropsWithChildren instead of children prop
- Use T[] instead of Array<T>
- Do not use {} for empty objects, use Record<string, never>
- Do not use the enum keyword, use `as const` instead
